
Feature: Percuit Website Student-Connect-Forums
 
Background:
Given the Student is authenticated in the system
    And the Student is on the “Forum” page
    And the student clicks on the "New Post" button
@wip
Scenario: Student cancels post creation
 Given the student is on the "Create a New Topic" page
 When the student enters a valid title
 And clicks the "Cancel" button
 Then the user should be redirected back to the “Forums” page
  And no new post should be created

@wip
Scenario: Student creates a new post successfully
    Given the student is on the "Create a New Topic" page
    When the student enters a valid title
    And the student enters or select valid tag
    And the student enters valid content
    And the student clicks "Create Topic" button
    Then the post should be created successfully
    And the user should see a success message
    And the new post should appear in the forum list
